    "notes": "A forgiving evolution of Scott Rao's blooming profile. Works with wide range of grind settings. The bloom ends when pressure drops from 4 to 2 bar, adapting to grind size. Extraction pressure adapts based on flow rate evolution. Developed for light roasts with large flat burrs. Temperature 88C - increase for very light roasts, decrease to 84-86C for darker roasts.",
